							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="97r" to="123r"/>
								<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Bava metsi῾a</title>
							</msItem>
							<msItem rend="v">
								<locus from="123r" to="165r"/>
								<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Bava batra</title>
								<note>
									<p>At the end of this treatise there are short notes on the order of the Tanaim and Amoraim (folios 162v and 163r) and on the treatment on horeg nefesh (folio 164r and 165r), besides several other brief remarks.</p>
								</note>
							</msItem>
